trans-unit.source: Provides a utility string class that is used by the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ObjectStateFormatter"></xref> class to optimize object graph serialization.
trans-unit.target: 提供公用程式的字串類別，以供<xref href="System.Web.UI.ObjectStateFormatter"></xref>最佳化物件圖形序列化的類別。

trans-unit.source: The IndexedString class is used by the <xref:System.Web.UI.ObjectStateFormatter> class to build string tables and optimize object graph serialization.
trans-unit.target: IndexedString 類別會由<xref:System.Web.UI.ObjectStateFormatter>類別來建置字串資料表及最佳化物件圖形序列化。</xref:System.Web.UI.ObjectStateFormatter>

trans-unit.source: IndexedString provides optimization that allows the efficient storing of page state information that contains a repeated string.
trans-unit.target: IndexedString 提供最佳化，可讓您有效率地儲存的頁面狀態資訊，其中包含重複的字串。

trans-unit.source: The IndexedString class is not intended to be used directly from your code.
trans-unit.target: IndexedString 類別不是直接從您的程式碼使用。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.IndexedString"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="System.Web.UI.IndexedString"></xref>類別。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.IndexedString> constructor ensures that the string passed is not `null` or <xref:System.String.Empty>, and then assigns it to the <xref:System.Web.UI.IndexedString.Value%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.IndexedString>建構函式可確保傳入的字串不是`null`或<xref:System.String.Empty>，然後將其指派給和<xref:System.Web.UI.IndexedString.Value%2A>屬性。</xref:System.Web.UI.IndexedString.Value%2A> </xref:System.String.Empty> </xref:System.Web.UI.IndexedString>

trans-unit.source: The string parameter passed to the constructor is <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> or <xref:System.String?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: 傳遞到建構函式的字串參數為<xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>或<xref:System.String?displayProperty=fullName>。

trans-unit.source: Gets the string associated with the <xref href="System.Web.UI.IndexedString"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: 取得相關聯的字串<xref href="System.Web.UI.IndexedString"></xref>物件。
